# Form Patterns

## Input Styling
```tsx
<input className="w-full rounded-md border bg-background px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring" />
```

## Labels
```tsx
<label className="mb-1 block text-xs font-medium md:text-sm">Label</label>
```

## Textarea with Character Count
```tsx
<div className="relative">
  <textarea maxLength={2000} className="w-full resize-none rounded-md border bg-background px-3 pb-5 pt-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring" />
  <span className="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-1.5 right-2 text-[10px] text-muted-foreground md:bottom-2 md:text-xs">
    {value.length}/2000
  </span>
</div>
```

## Submit Button
```tsx
<button type="submit" disabled={submitting || !field.trim()}
  className="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-primary px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 disabled:opacity-50">
  {submitting ? "Saving..." : "Save"}
</button>
```

## Error Display
```tsx
{error && <div className="text-xs text-destructive md:text-sm">{error}</div>}
```

## Form Layout (Sidebar Pattern)
```tsx
<div className="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[3fr,400px]">
  <div>{/* List content */}</div>
  <div className="lg:sticky lg:top-6 lg:self-start">
    <FeatureForm onSubmit={handleCreate} />
  </div>
</div>
```

## User Autocomplete
Two components exist for user input:
- `UserSearchPicker` (`@/components/todos`) — for todo assignment, returns `UserInfo`
- `UserSuggestInput` (`@/components/puzzles`) — for puzzle "completed by" text, fetches suggestions from `/api/users`
